{"text_id":17709,"tokens":["The"," debate"," over"," whether"," summer"," projects"," should"," be"," designed"," by"," teachers"," or"," students"," has"," been"," a"," longstanding"," controversy"," in"," the"," educational"," realm","."," While"," some"," argue"," that"," teacher","-","designed"," projects"," promote"," structure"," and"," accountability",","," others"," believe"," that"," student","-","designed"," projects"," foster"," creativity"," and"," autonomy","."," As"," an"," educator",","," I"," firmly"," believe"," that"," student","-","designed"," summer"," projects"," are"," more"," effective"," in"," preparing"," students"," for"," the"," upcoming"," school"," year",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," primary"," benefits"," of"," student","-","designed"," projects"," is"," that"," they"," promote"," creativity"," and"," problem","-","solving"," skills","."," When"," students"," are"," given"," the"," freedom"," to"," design"," their"," own"," projects",","," they"," are"," encouraged"," to"," think"," critically"," and"," outside"," the"," box","."," This"," not"," only"," enhances"," their"," creative"," abilities"," but"," also"," develops"," their"," problem","-","solving"," skills",","," as"," they"," learn"," to"," navigate"," obstacles"," and"," overcome"," challenges",".","\n\n","On"," the"," other"," hand",","," teacher","-","designed"," projects"," can"," often"," feel"," standardized"," and"," lack","luster",","," as"," students"," are"," given"," rigid"," guidelines"," and"," parameters"," to"," follow","."," This"," can"," be"," demo","tiv","ating"," for"," some"," students",","," particularly"," those"," who"," thrive"," on"," independence"," and"," autonomy","."," In"," contrast",","," student","-","designed"," projects"," allow"," students"," to"," take"," ownership"," of"," their"," learning",","," giving"," them"," a"," sense"," of"," agency"," and"," control"," over"," their"," academic"," pursuits",".","\n\n","Another"," significant",